# BYO-key model: users enter their Typhoon API key in the in-app onboarding
# screen, and it's stored in their browser's localStorage. The server does NOT
# need TYPHOON_API_KEY — the proxy reads the key from each request's
# Authorization header.
#
# Set TYPHOON_BASE_URL only if you self-host Typhoon or use a non-default
# endpoint. Defaults to https://api.opentyphoon.ai/v1
# TYPHOON_BASE_URL=https://api.opentyphoon.ai/v1
